Q 2. What are the pros and cons of a star schema compared to a snowflake schema?
 Star Schema vs  Snowflake Schema
 Star Schema — Pros

✔ Simple structure 
✔ Fast query performance 
✔ BI tools best use (Power BI, Tableau etc.)
✔ Reporting easy

 Star Schema — Cons

❌ Data redundancy (same data repeat hota hai)
❌ Storage thoda zyada lagta hai

 Snowflake Schema — Pros

✔ No redundancy (normalized tables)
✔ Data consistency better
✔ Storage efficient

 Snowflake Schema — Cons

❌ Complex structure
❌ More joins → slow queries
❌ Query likhna tough

| Feature     | Star Schema | Snowflake Schema |
| ----------- | ----------- | ---------------- |
| Structure   | Simple      | Complex          |
| Performance | Fast        | Slow             |
| Joins       | Less        | More             |
| Redundancy  | Yes         | No               |
| Storage     | More        | Less             |
| Use Case    | Reporting   | Data consistency |
